title: Brian Kemp - Wikipedia
snippet: There was speculation that he would run in the 2026 United States Senate election in Georgia to challenge incumbent senator Jon Ossoff; in May 2025, he declined to run and endorsed Derek Dooley. Kemp was inaugurated as governor in a public ceremony in Atlanta on January 14, 2019.
